dimanche ( english : sunday ) is a canadian animated short film by patrick &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . the film debuted at the berlin international film festival in february 2011 and online on january 5 , 2012 . dimanche is the first professional film by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , a native of montreal . &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; had previously created a three-minute animated short square roots in 2006 , while enrolled in the nfb 's &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; program for young animators . still learning how to use computer animation tools , he worked with pen and pencil to create dimanche , hand drawing the entire film . the 10-minute film took him two years to complete , creating individual drawings on paper , working on a light table . &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ended up with 15 boxes full of sheets with sketches , which he then scanned into the computer , &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and began editing . &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; believes such traditional animation techniques are better for portraying emotion .